Eve: I added side1 and side2. Eventually this has to be overhauled, so that there is a NONVIEWPOINTED War frame as well as a viewpointed one that is Invaded good guys vs. Invader bad guys.  But side1 and side2 are being linked to Competition.competitors.
ALSO War should have an x-schema that can be mapped onto the Competition x-schema, and winner and loser roles that map onto the winner and loser roles in the Competition frame, and an Outcome that maps onto Outcome in Competition, and...

Elise: now that the Competition frames are revamped, this needs to be overhauled as well.
